    rdfs:comment "Are brief discharges with a very steep upslope and shallow fall that occur in all leads which include that electrode." ;
    heda:suggestedTag hedt:Artifact-significance-to-recording ;
    hed:hasHedParent hedt:Non-biological-artifact .

